blog.name: askdawnandvern
blog.title: Ask Dawn and Vern!
blog.description: Oh um, hello. I'm Dawn Bellwether. Yes, 'THAT' Dawn Bellwether. Ex-Assistant Mayor, Ex-Mayor, Ex-Criminal Mastermind, City Savior, Controversial Author and Predator/Prey Relationship Advocate. With the release of my book, "Predator seeking Prey", I've been getting a lot of public attention again. With that came a lot of questions. Vernon, my best friend and mate, thought it would be a good idea to deal with it directly by opening a blog and taking questions about our lives and our friends lives directly. So feel free to ask us questions...I guess?   (Blog Author Note: This blog is based on the story "The Rehabilitation of Dawn Bellwether" Which you can find on Fanfiction.net by yours truly WastedTimeEE. Aside from taking questions I am currently writing a sequel to the story which is in progress. This is my first time doing an ask blog and I hope you all like it. Oh, I'll also take questions too. Please donate to my Patreon.) Wasted Time's Patreon!

summary: And at last I see the light And it's like the fog has lifted And at last I see the light And it's like the sky is new And it's...
caption:
And at last I see the light
And it’s like the fog has lifted
And at last I see the light
And it’s like the sky is new
And it’s warm and real and bright
And the world has somehow shifted
All at once everything looks different
Now that I see you

———————-

Been wanting to do this for a while. I love Tangled. It’s my second favourite Disney princess movie and I always thought that Tamara and Ookami fitted Flynn and Rapunzel the best out of all of the Disney couples. One is a sweet girl and the other is a charming guy.


Couldn’t be bother with shading so I left it like this

This picture has oc x canon stuff in it so if that is not your cup of tea then leave.
